<br>
So, while the potential is there, i would advise you to find groups as much as you can, and revert to soloing when you are alone and cant. Will it mean you rise to 50 a little slower ? Possibly yes. But then again, it is all new to you. You didnt run through the levels with x other characters. If you treat every level as something new, which allows you to see places you didnt see before, gettign to 50 might be as much fun as being at 50.<br>
<br>
Will other necros be better at soloing than you ? Quite definately. But its not a contest of wether you are the best solo Necromancer or not. That, you could have on any of the other servers. Here it can also be about how your character is as a person.<br>
<br>
On a side note - the fastest experience i got was when being grouped. In some cases, it was very surprising, just how fast it was. I honestly think it is a myth that you have to solo to rise fastest. It is possible that if you know all ins and outs, and have pervect equipment, going solo is fastest. But many out there dont have either. <p>Silenae Do'Bauthin<br><br>
